<br />\n所以我較鬧鐘不停咁響<br />\n之後我阿哥就將佢自己個鬧鐘兜野掉落我個頭度<br />\n嗰日個頭腫住咁返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n報串俾老母知炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有一次屎忽痕偷偷地張我著過成日既底褲放入佢個枕頭套入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港幾熱大家都清楚啦，嗰陣仲要係未減肥既時候，大髀拿個位真係清香撲鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兩日之後我工人拎住條底褲問佢佢先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢一路打鳩我，我一路笑鳩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打您真係仆街嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17fd6c266450474d9377547952736efd12ba7a70","tid":186673,"uid":15174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>偷錢<br />\n屋企邊度有錢就偷</blockquote><br />\n呢個要教...教唔好就要打"},{"pid":"1c57f89168c6e41fa135150f9f9e6b47cec8d7d6","tid":186673,"uid":21585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T13:12:31.000Z","msg":"我家姐好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係有時成個老母咁教訓我姐"}]}